highlights.text: “ฝากไว้ให้ Kiss (feat. BLVCKHEART)” by JayQ and BLVCKHEART is the highest new entry on Top Songs Thailand at #149.
YOUNGOHM has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “เจิดจรัส” is the highest at #7.
“ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 960 days straight.
“ฉันรู้ดี” by Spoonfulz is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 64 spots at #116.
